the love eterne is a 1963 hong kong musical film of the huangmei opera genre directed by li han hsiang .   an adaptation of the classic chinese story " butterfly lovers " , it tells of the doomed romance between the male liang shanbo ( portrayed by actress ivy ling po , who also sang the character 's vocals ) and the cross-dressed female zhu yingtai ( betty loh ti , with singing dubbed by tsin ting ) .   the film won 6 awards at the 2nd golden horse awards in taiwan , including best picture .   it was also selected as hong kong 's entry for the best foreign language film at the 36th academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee .